  "text": [
    "Ken Coombs, a member of the club passed away.  His family has asked if any of the members of the club would be interested in any of his old gear.",
    "Like most of us, he aquired lots of stuff.",
    "If anyone is interest, please let me know and I can put you in touch with Samantha Crowley, his daughter in law."
